alerts.headline: Rip Current Statement issued September 23 at 3:14PM EDT until September 24 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Boston
alerts.description:
...HIGH RIP CURRENT RISK IN EFFECT THROUGH FRIDAY EVENING...
* WHAT...Dangerous rip currents.
* WHERE...Eastern Essex MA, Suffolk MA, Eastern Norfolk MA,
Eastern Plymouth MA, Southern Plymouth MA and Barnstable MA
Counties.
* WHEN...Through Friday evening.
* IMPACTS...Rip currents can sweep even the best swimmers away
from shore into deeper water.
